<sect1 id="dir_f62186ca603740537cec9464f8799975_1autotoc_md312">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::scoring::systems</title><para>Systems for score processing and observation.</para>
<para>This namespace contains systems that handle scoring events, update score observers, and manage score state lifecycle.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_f62186ca603740537cec9464f8799975_1autotoc_md313">
<title>Systems</title><para><table rows="4" cols="3"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>System  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Phase  </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>Description  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>CombatScoringSystem</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Update  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Processes death events and issues score commands  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>ScoreObserverSystem</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Update  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Syncs ScoreObserverComponent values from ScorePools  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>ScoreObserverClearSystem</computeroutput>  </para>
