<sect1 id="dir_f62186ca603740537cec9464f8799975_1autotoc_md314">
<title>Execution Order</title><para>1. <bold>CombatScoringSystem</bold> - Listens for <computeroutput>DeathEvent</computeroutput>, checks for <computeroutput>ScoreValueComponent</computeroutput>, issues <computeroutput>UpdateScoreCommand</computeroutput> 2. <bold>ScoreObserverSystem</bold> - Reads from <computeroutput>ScorePool</computeroutput> and updates <computeroutput>ScoreObserverComponent.value</computeroutput> 3. <bold>ScoreObserverClearSystem</bold> - Clears <computeroutput>hasUpdate</computeroutput> flag after UI systems have processed changes</para>
